   <strong>Discount</strong> = 6% of $1200 = <sup>6</sup>&frasl;<sub>100</sub> x <sup>1200</sup>&frasl;<sub>1</sub> = 6 x 12 = <strong>$72</strong>
    <br>
    The actual price = $1200 - $72 = <strong>$1128</strong>
    
    </div>
